Welcome to Town Of Us Reworked %modversion%!

Town Of Us Reactivated but better! (hopefully)

This mod is a mish mash of code and ideas from different games, mods and forks, mainly from Town Of Salem, Town Of Us Reactivated and The Other Roles. Enjoy the chaos that comes out as a result!

If you want to know more try using the other info commands, visiting the %github% page or joining the %discord% server. Happy ejections!

Changelog-
- Mega Addition: Completely recoded the asset management system, now you can customise the mod's icons however you wish!
- Addition: Added some more visual indicators for player statuses
- Optimisation: Optimised the code to run better
- Recode: Recoded client options
- Buff: Monarch is now alerted when a knight is attacked
- Buff: Jackal can now kill directly when all of their recruits are dead (including the third one)
- Buff: Glitch hacks can now render your defense useless (unless you are an Apocalypse role)
- Change: Guesses now count as an interaction, making guessers susceptible to being doused or infected
- Improvement: Greatly reduced the time it takes to load a lot of things
- Improvement: Improved how random maps are selected
- Critical Fix: The game should no longer crash during the loading screen for lower end PCs
- Role Fix: Fixed Monarch having permanent defense for as long as they have knighted someone
- Role Fix: Fixed converted Mystics not being able to turn into Seers
- Role Fix: Fixed Grenadier not flashing during their first attempt at blinding people
- Role Fix: Fixed Bastion bombs bypassing defense
- Role Fix: Fixed the Guesser guess menu being bugged out
- Role Fix: Protect uses now sync correctly between the alive and grave protect buttons for Guardian Angel
- Objectifier Fix: Fixed the Allied faction not syncing correctly
- Bug Fix: Fixed role generation sometimes freaking out
- Bug Fix: Fixed being able to call sabotages when blinded
- Bug Fix: Fixed teleports behaving weirdly sometimes
- Bug Fix: Fixed clicking on the report button using your ability instead
- Bug Fix: Fixed some more log spams (these things haunt me I swear)
- Bug Fix: Fixed Submerged breaking with the mod active
- Bug Fix: Fixed the Presets menu sometimes overlapping
- Bug Fix: Fixed the overlapping issue with client side options
- Bug Fix: Fixed some minor issues here and there
- Visual Fix: Fixed the role card incorrectly showing your attack and defense values sometimes
- Visual Fix: Fixed animations for jumping out of a vent not playing
- General Fix: Clarified a lot of outdated/missing information
- Removed: Removed the region installer from the mod, it's better being used in Mini's mod

